data.description: Introducing a charming 3-bedroom home in Osakis, close to schools and the ball field. Recently updated with a new kitchen, bathroom, and premium vinyl plank flooring, it offers modern living. Enjoy main floor convenience with a primary bedroom, walk-in shower, and laundry. Stay comfortable and efficient with a new furnace, central air, and solar system. Outside, find practical features like gutter guards, a welcoming front deck, vinyl siding and windows, a durable concrete driveway, and a 50 amp connection for an RV hookup. A large 10 x 16 storage shed for added storage convenience. Ideal for first-time buyers or those seeking a retirement haven, this property offers versatility and value. Positioned on a generous corner lot, there's ample space to envision the addition of a garage, completing this charming and functional residence.
